title: Some torture tests fail on x86_64-apple-darwin20.1.0
body:

### Platform
macos big sur
version 11.0.1

### Code

Failures are from:

- rust/compile/torture/block_expr1.rs
- rust/compile/torture/empty_main.rs
- rust/compile/torture/exit_error.rs
- rust/compile/torture/func1.rs

### Meta

- latest master as of 17 Jun 2021 - be78228790d125fe46af339d6b323a6a545f278f
